  <heading>UQCVTN</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Unsigned 32-bit integer saturating extract narrow to interleaved 16-bit integer</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction saturates the unsigned integer value in each element of the pair of
source vectors to half the original source element width,
and places the two-way interleaved results in the half-width destination elements.</para>
      <para>This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
  </desc>
